{"tid":1995190,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「五區公投」走數？　鄭松泰：我都想實現　笑言自己「好nice」","createTime":"2020-04-30T05:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T13:43:20.000Z","uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"450eb32e9f33e1bd538d5f69bf0f9652bd7ed013","tid":1995190,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:11:18.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">「熱普城」選舉聯盟主打「五區公投 全民制憲 永續基本法」，最終只得熱血公民鄭松泰勝出。他早上於商台節目直言「有少少孤單」，又強調自己不是不結交「朋友」，笑言：「我份人好nice架！」</code></pre><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">問到是否「走數」，他指「我都其實想實現」，稱若有5名同道人進入立法會，他樂意推動，「（主持問：有無信心說服到其他人？）暫時大家焦點喺橫洲，無睇到2047咁遠。（主持問：所以要交朋友）我唔係唔交朋友，我份人好nice架」。</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20160926/s00001/1474863113304/「五區公投」走數-鄭松泰-我都想實現-笑言自己「好nice」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20160926%2Fs00001%2F1474863113304%2F%E3%80%8C%E4%BA%94%E5%8D%80%E5%85%AC%E6%8A%95%E3%80%8D%E8%B5%B0%E6%95%B8-%E9%84%AD%E6%9D%BE%E6%B3%B0-%E6%88%91%E9%83%BD%E6%83%B3%E5%AF%A6%E7%8F%BE-%E7%AC%91%E8%A8%80%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E3%80%8C%E5%A5%BDnice%E3%80%8D&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ8tNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=69389171\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20160926%2Fs00001%2F1474863113304%2F%E3%80%8C%E4%BA%94%E5%8D%80%E5%85%AC%E6%8A%95%E3%80%8D%E8%B5%B0%E6%95%B8-%E9%84%AD%E6%9D%BE%E6%B3%B0-%E6%88%91%E9%83%BD%E6%83%B3%E5%AF%A6%E7%8F%BE-%E7%AC%91%E8%A8%80%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E3%80%8C%E5%A5%BDnice%E3%80%8D&h=3d147ecf\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20160926/s00001/1474863113304/「五區公投」走數-鄭松泰-我都想實現-笑言自己「好nice」</a>"},{"pid":"eb904fa3e0085e6b3a41fc3dd1dddffb03345c13","tid":1995190,"uid":118520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"450eb32e9f33e1bd538d5f69bf0f9652bd7ed013","tid":1995190,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:11:18.000Z","msg":"<pre><c